This is a wonderful sauce that i have been making for years. Great comfort food, especially in the winter. I agree its better to use a short tubular pasta to hold the sauce better. I add the eggplant back into the sauce before its done to allow the flavors to meld. I also use basil instead of oregano and top each serving with small pieces of fresh mozzarella - it melts nicely from the heat of the sauce.

